>潘建雄</div>\n                                <div class=\"tposition\">博士、助理教授</div>\n                                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"tcontent\">\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>博士生导师</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>电  话: 010-62772053</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>邮  箱: panpan@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                   <p></p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                        </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu\">  \n                     \n       <li class=\"on\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教育背景</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">工作经历</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教学工作</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究领域</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术成果</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术兼职</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n    </ul> \n    \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-on\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2013.08-2019.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，获得核科学与技术专业博士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2009.08-2013.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，获得核工程与核技术专业学士学位</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n</div></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2022.01-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，助理教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2019.07-2021.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，博士后</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">讲授《核燃料与核材料》本科生课程</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">讲授《核燃料循环工艺》、《同位素分离》研究生课程</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">指导学生情况：指导硕士毕业生2人；在读硕士生2人，博士生3人</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">主要从事同位素分离及相关技术研究</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. 周文必，胡子帆，潘建雄*，姜东君.多组分同位素分离级联的数值优化方法研究[J].同位素,2024,37(03):211-217.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. 孙旺，周明胜，姜东君，潘建雄*.以SiH4为介质扩散法生产28Si技术研究[J].同位素,2024,37(03):203-210.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. Zhou W, Huang D, Pan J, et al. Numerical study on the performance and internal flow of centrifugal impeller under external cooling conditions[C]//6th Chinese International Turbomachinery Conference (CITC 2024). IET, 2024, 2024: 45-52. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4. 黄东洋，周文必，姜东君，潘建雄. 入口压强对离心式压缩机性能影响的数值研究[J].清华大学学报(自然科学版),2024,64(09):1666-1676</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">5. 孙旺;潘建雄;周明胜;孙启明;王彦博. ~(76)Ge同位素的离心级联分离制备[J]. 原子能科学技术,2022，56(08): 1714-1720</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2025年5月-至今，《同位素》青年编委</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div clas